//Doom
@60081 = ~Wand of Doom~
@60082 = ~When activated, this wand causes a feeling of doom to overwhelm the target. For the duration of the spell, the target receives a -2 penalty to all <PRO_HISHER> rolls, including THAC0 and Saving Throws. There is no Saving Throw for this spell.

