 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


//Faerie Fire
@60083 = ~Wand of Faerie Fire~
@60084 = ~Upon uttering the activation phrase, this wand outlines one or more creatures with a pale violet glow, making positions and movements easily visible. Outlined creatures are easier to strike, giving them an Armor Class penalty of -2.

