@60124 = ~Wand of Ghoul Touch~
@60125 = ~When the wielder activates this wand, a green glow encompasses <PRO_HISHER> hand. If the wielder makes a successful melee attack against a creature, the creature must make a Save vs. Wand or be paralyzed for 6 rounds.

STATISTICS:
(Necromancy)

Charge abilities:
– Ghoul Touch
